  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWe've made changes at some points to our monorepo that break CI for projects using our monorepo (e.g. changing the L2 gasPrice from 0 to 1 gwei) including Synthetix and Chainlink\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nRun the Synthetix OVM integration tests and Chainlink OVM Integration tests once a day in *our* CI and alert if they do not pass.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nSynthetix had been added at one point: https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/integration-tests/pull/69\r\n",
